Cell["\<\
Note the \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]carry-in = carry-out\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] \
highlights, which justifies leaving that much of the I-Cats compressed.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.97939471592717*^9, 3.9793947348154373`*^9}, {
  3.9793974919803905`*^9, 
  3.979397550969385*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"bd5ccacf-e927-9c42-b82b-\
b925e15656da"],

Cell["\<\
Why unpack one each of the I-Cats?  There was one extra digit in the leading \
position of the I-Cat argument, after multiplying by the multiplier, so (at \
least) one column carries are guaranteed.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.979245531797024*^9, 3.9792456165857353`*^9}, {
  3.97939757228244*^9, 
  3.9793976872870007`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"b73c0a37-0ab0-b349-bf73-\
5bf102e5a445"],

