Cell["\<\
4(2) generates no carries, no needed preliminary 0 column. 4(3) and 4(4) \
trigger a 1-digit carry, unpack one copy -- of which?  The current I-Cat, or \
the previous one?!\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.979397756712124*^9, 
